data.title: Physical Map Of Europe
data.meta_description: Physical Map Of Europe - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: The document lists major physical features to add to a map of Europe, including rivers depicted as blue lines, seas, relief features shown as brown shading, and an extension task to add additional seas, relief areas, rivers, the Arctic Circle, and volcanoes. It provides rivers such as the Thames, Tagus, Rhone, Rhine, Danube, Seine, and Po. Seas include the Atlantic Ocean, North Sea, English Channel, Mediterranean Sea, Adriatic Sea, Black Sea, and Baltic Sea. Relief features comprise the Scandinavian Mountains, North European Plain, Pyrenees, Apennines, and Balkan Mountains. The extension task prompts adding 3 more seas, 3 more relief areas, 3
